title: How to Make Lots of Mulch on Binweevils

steps.headline: Spend most of your mulch on plants.
steps.description: Make sure to fill up your whole garden! The best kind of plants are most rare plants or plant Helicopter swedes if you are a Bin Tycoon, and plant Bubble Plants until level 41.

steps.headline: Complete your daily activities.
steps.description: Daily activities typically earn you mulch. They include The Daily Brain Drain, Spot the Difference, Catch it Bin it Kill it, Whack a weevil, Mulch Shoot and The Smoothie Shack game if you're a Bin Tycoon.

steps.headline: Race.
steps.description: You can race at tracks one, two, and three to earn mulch. Track 2 is usually most popular.

steps.headline: Play games.
steps.description: Games such as Connect Mulch, Pool, and Squares can be found at Castle Gam, Dosh's Palace, Club Fling, inside Tink's Tree, and more.

steps.headline: Water Mushrooms at Flum's Fountain.
steps.description: Watering Mushrooms will not only get you mulch! (tycoons only)You can also get Happiness, XP (experience points), and fitness!

steps.headline: Activate your account if you haven't already done so and if you need to help a Bin Tycoon get mulch waste all your mulch in their plaza, the easiest way is buying pictures in their photo studio if they have one.
